{"id": "1417459936497111120", "channel_id": "1417459936497111120", "type": 0, "author_id": "761032725666725888", "author_name": "dittoqwq", "author_bot": false, "content": "感觉很适合做扑克牌之类的设计就做了。怎么说呢，就是我觉得他喝下酒的那刻真的很帅，有种视死如归的感觉！所以呢，就搞了个这玩意。唉，第一次画这样的画面，比例不对的话非常抱歉！第二张是骷髅头的，想塞进画面里但感觉有点违和感哈哈。真的很喜欢杜勒赛因呀💙💙\n黑桃好像是象征死亡的意思（至少我谷歌是这么说的）\n\nuid：100425926", "timestamp": "2025-09-16T10:39:43.993000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-16T10:43:06.587000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "thinking2", "emoji_id": "1356053172065534153", "count": 6}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1417459937159675914", "filename": "IMG_0579.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1163191, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417459936497111120/1417459937159675914/IMG_0579.jpg?ex=69cba470&is=69ca52f0&hm=cdf201ba7e5baa3eb80a3846658934f9578f597287b824bd5bb68b9f4341b601&"}, {"id": "1417459937965248573", "filename": "IMG_0581.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1269536, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417459936497111120/1417459937965248573/IMG_0581.jpg?ex=69cba470&is=69ca52f0&hm=0680c8750fc915c374339137ee093dd073ffa4c6e74dcafd498d4031f8c52643&"}, {"id": "1417459938615234582", "filename": "IMG_0580.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1161277, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417459936497111120/1417459938615234582/IMG_0580.jpg?ex=69cba470&is=69ca52f0&hm=c3b79ab00a5a4939f481e36db01e554a31abf110d7f087bb33a89d7c59e65f62&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417459936497111120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "画了杜勒赛因的卡牌！", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1395992145638330368", "1182359773723754537"]}
